[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "潮の引きにより現れた海底洞窟……\nもしかしたら、ここが伝承の……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "本当に、海の底にこんな場所が……！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "あたしも初めてだよ、こんな場所。\nなんか、ワクワクしてきた！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "足元、滑りやすいから気を付けて。\n無駄に転ばないでよ、シャル",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "もう、ミルカ！　\nあたしだって慎重に歩くよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "……ここ、なんだか空気がひんやりしてますね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "伝承通りなら、この奥にお宝が眠っているはず。\nただ、その場合――",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "お宝を守る恐ろしい魔物もいるとのことでしたよね……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "うわあっ！　向こうになんかいるよ！！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "きゃあっ！　あれは……大きい、牙！？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……よく見て。あれは鉱石よ。\n洞窟を囲うような配列のせいで、牙のように見えるだけ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "まるで大きく口を開けた竜が、牙を覗かせて、\n私たちを奥へと誘っているみたいだわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "……伝承にあった「竜が招き入れる」っていうのは、\nもしかしたら、ここのことかもしれないわね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "おお……！　つまり、ここが伝承の場所かもしれない！\nこれは超期待できるね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "進もう。何かあったら、すぐ戻ること。\n無理はしないで",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "静かに。\n……何か、気配がする",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "えっ……\nもしかして、お宝を守る魔物ですか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "分からないけれど……水音が増えてる。\n何かが近づいてるのかも",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "交戦の準備はできてる",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "慌てないで。\n……ここからは慎重に進む",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "わ、分かりました……！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……姉さん、先頭お願い。\n姉さんの嗅覚、こういう時は役立つから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ええ、任せて。\n……みんな、ついてきて",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]